25. What is SCP and How Does It Work?
ï¿½ï¿½ SCP = String Constant Pool
Â·Â 
Special memory area inside Method Area (before Java 8)Â or Heap (Java 8+)
Â·Â 
Avoids creating duplicate strings
Â·Â 
Uses intern()Â to reuse strings
Â·Â 
String a = "Java";
String b = "Java";
System.out.println(a == b); // true (same reference)



