9. What is Deadlock?
ï¿½ï¿½ DeadlockÂ occurs when two threads hold a lock and wait for each other's lock.
// Thread A locks obj1, waits for obj2
// Thread B locks obj2, waits for obj1
ï¿½ï¿½ Avoid usingÂ nested locks and always acquire locks in the same order.



